<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.5.10">
<l>uṇṭu mumiḻntuṅ kaṭantu miṭantuṅ kiṭantuniṉṟum</l>
<l>koṇṭa kōlat toṭuvīṟ ṟiruntu maṇaṅkūṭiyum</l>
<l>kaṇṭa vāṟṟā ṟaṉakkē yulakeṉa niṉṟāṉṟaṉṉai</l>
<l>vaṇṭamiḻ nūṟka nōṟṟē ṉaṭiyārk kiṉpamāriyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>On him who, having swallowed, spit out, churned, scooped out, lied, stood,</l>
<l>sat in distinction with the attire he took, having joined in union,</l>
<l>stood thinking the world is his alone by the way he see [it],</l>
<l>I have done penance I order to spin a [poem] in generous Tamil: showers of bliss for [his] servants.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
